She sighed and knew Black Aracnia was right.  But that didn't calm 
her fears any.  "Black Aracnia, If Quickstrike and I go back, 
megatron may kill us for the fun of it.  He's like that.  Haven't you 
delt with him before? You know what he is like." She threw her arms 
in the air and walked to the wall.  She punched the wall as hard as 
she could a fw times till her knuckles bled.  They healed up in a 
second as if no damage was done to them.
